  <brief_title>The Effects of Amino Acid Supplement During Acute Inflammation.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Metabolic Effects of Endotoxin Induced Acute Inflammation in Healthy Young Men With and Without Supplement of Amino Acids.</official_title>
